{"type":"text","timestamp":1773482859257,"sessionID":"ses_3143284c2ffeAaKW1jZQzt4vTf","part":{"id":"prt_cebd0bdab002zIYV0svmQXaAgS","sessionID":"ses_3143284c2ffeAaKW1jZQzt4vTf","messageID":"msg_cebd0b5eb001ocCQzbXaOUJ0Ga","type":"text","text":"All tasks complete. Here's a summary of what was implemented:\n\n## Summary\n\n### New file: `src/lib/tui-wishlist.ts`\nCreated `WishlistOverlay` class — a blessed modal popup overlay that:\n- Shows wishlist items in a scrollable list with item text, tags, and `created_at` timestamp\n- **A key**: Opens a textbox input to add a new item (persisted via `wishlist-store.ts`)\n- **D/X keys**: Deletes the currently selected item\n- **Escape/W keys**: Closes the overlay (W acts as toggle)\n- Follows the established pattern from `tui-question-popup.ts` (modal overlay on a blessed screen with shadow, border styling, and `onClose` callback)\n\n### Modified: `src/lib/tui-quest-picker.ts`\n- Added `WishlistOverlay` import\n- Added `wishlistOverlay` private field to track the overlay instance\n- Added **W keybind** in `bindKeys()` to toggle the wishlist overlay\n- Added `toggleWishlist()` method that opens/closes the overlay\n- Updated status bar to show `W wishlist` key hint\n\n### Modified: `src/lib/tui-browser.ts`\n- Added `WishlistOverlay` import\n- Added `wishlistOverlay` private field to track the overlay instance\n- Added **W keybind** in `bindKeys()` to toggle the wishlist overlay\n- Added `toggleWishlist()` method that opens/closes the overlay\n- Updated status bar to show `W wishlist` key hint\n\n### Verification\n- `bun run typecheck` — passes cleanly\n- `bun run build` — passes cleanly (1.30 MB bundle, 178 modules)","time":{"start":1773482859256,"end":1773482859256}}}
